and do something

00:02:09.995 --> 00:02:12.198
like a traditional
plantation wedding...

00:02:12.231 --> 00:02:14.534
Traditional...

00:02:14.567 --> 00:02:17.737
1790... traditional?

00:02:17.770 --> 00:02:19.972
-Absolutely.
-Because we're gonna dress up

00:02:20.005 --> 00:02:22.375
our little cousins, like,
you know, little slaves,

00:02:22.408 --> 00:02:24.477
-little... little (bleep)
running around. -Yeah.

00:02:24.510 --> 00:02:25.912
-You know what I mean?
-Aw...

00:02:25.945 --> 00:02:27.213
And we might beat 'em.

00:02:27.246 --> 00:02:28.915
-With, like, Nerf whips.
-Everybody take turns.

00:02:28.948 --> 00:02:31.417
-Not real whips.
-Yeah, not real whips.

