Absolutely. Yes.

00:02:47.933 --> 00:02:49.902
I'm... I am the owner
of the property,

00:02:49.935 --> 00:02:52.805
-I am not the owner of you.
-Of us. Yeah.

00:02:52.838 --> 00:02:55.274
Oh. Well,
that should be on the sign.

00:02:55.307 --> 00:02:57.944
<i> Our approach might have been
 too traditional for Colleen,</i>

00:02:57.977 --> 00:03:00.179
<i> so we sat down
 with a black person</i>

00:03:00.212 --> 00:03:01.747
<i> to see how they would feel.</i>

